OL,3,CWhat's the deal with Olivia Attwood's
OL,4,C'marriage'?
OL,6,FSpoiler alert...not everything you see
OL,7,Fon TV is real (shock horror).
OL,9,FThat being said, when a reality show
OL,10,Ffollows a celebrity couple's journey
OL,11,Ffrom engagement to their wedding day,
OL,12,Fyou would kind of expect that to be
OL,13,Fauthentic.
OL,15,FEnter Olivia Attwood and Bradley Dack,
OL,16,Fa reality star and football player
OL,17,Fcombination that had very much
OL,18,Finserted itself into the UK's famous
OL,19,Ffaces roster and filled countless
OL,20,Fcolumn inches and social media feeds.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
