OL,3,CWhat's the deal with Olivia Attwood's
OL,4,C'marriage'?
OL,6,FHowever, it now turns out (reportedly)
OL,7,Fthat the pair never actually signed on
OL,8,Fthe dotted line and certified their
OL,9,Fmarriage, leaving some fans and
OL,10,Fviewers feeling slightly duped.
OL,12,FLet's take a few steps back. Olivia
OL,13,FAttwood first found herself in the
OL,14,Fspotlight on Love Island in 2017.
OL,16,FSince then, she's established herself
OL,17,Fas a staple on ITV. The 34-year-old
OL,18,Fhas fronted documentaries, appeared on
OL,19,Freality shows and is a regular
OL,20,Fpanellist on Loose Women.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
