OL,3,CWhat's the deal with Olivia Attwood's
OL,4,C'marriage'?
OL,6,FIn 2019, Attwood got engaged to
OL,7,Ffootballer Bradley Dack. Given her
OL,8,Fhigh follower-count online and growing
OL,9,Fprominence on-screen, ITV commissioned
OL,10,Fa show to follow the couple's journey
OL,11,Fdown the aisle.
OL,13,FOlivia Meets Her Match & Olivia
OL,14,FMarries Her Match filmed a combined 17
OL,15,Fepisodes.
OL,17,FNow comes the drama! One that's a bit
OL,18,Flike a loose thread, the more you pick
OL,19,Fat it, the more it unravels.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
