OL,3,CWhat's the deal with Olivia Attwood's
OL,4,C'marriage'?
OL,6,FThe final episode of the series showed
OL,7,Fan opulent wedding in June 2023. No
OL,8,Fexpense spared as the couple 'tied the
OL,9,Fknot' at the Bvlgari Hotel in London.
OL,11,FAttwood and Dack split up earlier this
OL,12,Fyear. The reasons for which I'll let
OL,13,Fyou surmise from a deep dive on the
OL,14,Ftrusty ol' internet.
OL,16,FWhat's come to light since their split
OL,17,Fis that the fancy hotel they got
OL,18,F'married' at on camera almost three
OL,19,Fyears ago didn't have a marriage
OL,20,Flicence at the time.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
