OL,3,CWhat's the deal with Olivia Attwood's
OL,4,C'marriage'?
OL,6,FReports suggest that their wedding
OL,7,Fplanner tried to get one for the venue
OL,8,Fbut couldn't secure it in time.
OL,10,FSo, it's claimed an appointment was
OL,11,Fbooked to complete all the paperwork
OL,12,Fat a registry office in Cheshire, six
OL,13,Fweeks later.
OL,15,FHowever, this was cancelled after
OL,16,FAttwood allegedly discovered 'a number
OL,17,Fof mistruths', according to a source
OL,18,Ffamiliar with the situation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
