OL,3,CWhat's the deal with Olivia Attwood's
OL,4,C'marriage'?
OL,6,FWhat does that mean? Well, if the
OL,7,Frumours are true then they never
OL,8,Factually got married.
OL,10,FDespite Attwood using Dack's surname
OL,11,Fon-air and on her social media
OL,12,Fplatforms (until recently), the
OL,13,Fsuggestion is that since fans saw them
OL,14,Fget married, the duo have acted like
OL,15,Fthey're married, but that isn't the
OL,16,Fcase.
OL,18,FThey've no doubt benefited financially
OL,19,Ffrom the ITV show and the subsequent
OL,20,Fbelief that they are indeed husband
OL,21,Fand wife.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
