OL,3,CWhat's the deal with Olivia Attwood's
OL,4,C'marriage'?
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FITV has chosen not to comment on the
OL,12,Fissue, but it's being reported widely
OL,13,Fthat the broadcaster wasn't familiar
OL,14,Fthat their star presenter and her
OL,15,F'husband' weren't legally married
OL,16,Funtil the tabloid newspapers started
OL,17,Fwriting about it in late March 2026.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
