OL,3,CWhat's the deal with Olivia Attwood's
OL,4,C'marriage'?
OL,6,FWill ITV face any Ofcom complaints for
OL,7,Fmisleading viewers? Well, no...the
OL,8,Ftimeframe to complain about a show is
OL,9,F20 working days after it's been
OL,10,Fbroadcast, and ITV showed the
OL,11,Fprogramme the same year Attwood and
OL,12,FDack were believed to have gotten
OL,13,Fmarried, 2023.
OL,15,FSocial media comments would lead me to
OL,16,Fbelieve that many are displeased with
OL,17,Fthe revelations about the couple and
OL,18,Fcriticise them for not being more open
OL,19,Fand honest about what has allegedly
OL,20,Fhappened in the weeks/months/years
OL,21,Fsince their 'wedding.'
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
